org.pragmaticminds.crunch.api.windowed.extractor.aggregate

Interface Aggregation<T extends Serializable>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface Aggregation<T extends Serializable>
extends Serializable
    This abstract class accumulates all given values and returns am aggregated value, when called. It also has an identifier, which can be read or set.
    Author:
    Erwin Wagasow Created by Erwin Wagasow on 16.08.2018
